"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/855666","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2018-03-08","<p>The number of apprentices employed by this Department was 37 as of 28 February 2018. This equates to 2.2 per cent of the Department's directly employed headcount for the same date.<em><br></em></p>","Rossendale and Darwen","Jake Berry",,"2018-03-08T11:01:16.17Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/855666/answer","Biography information for Jake Berry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/855666/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/855666/answer",,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2018-03-05","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government: Apprentices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, how many and what proportion of the staff employed by his Department are apprentices.","false","Biography information for Angela Rayner","Ashton-under-Lyne","Angela Rayner","130973"
