use of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many people received relief on Stamp Duty Land Tax for demutualisation of an insurance company in (a) 2015-16, (b) 2016-17 and (c) 2017-18.","false","Biography information for Peter Dowd","Bootle","Peter Dowd","130598"
